snippet.title: Diana and Roma visited Mermaids of Arabia in Dubai. Magical Mermaid & Pirate transformation!
snippet.description:
Diana and Roma visited the Mermaid Boutique "Mermaids of Arabia" in Dubai. The Sea Fairies turned Diana into the Mermaid Princess. Roma dresses up as a real Pirate and hunts for treasures. Amazing adventure for kids Magical Mermaid & Pirate transformation!
Thanks for watching!
